<div class="cards">
	<div class="form-block">
		<h4>请按下面提示激活您的VIP卡 </h4>

		<p>请输入您的手机号码</p>

		<%=form_for :card, :url=>input_mobile_card_path do |f|%>
			<%=f.hidden_field :no,:value=>@card.no%>
			<div class="field">
				<label class="field-label "><span class="required">*</span>手机号码 : </label>
				<%=text_field_tag :tel,@card.member_card&&@card.member_card.user_tel,:class=>"field-input sms_tel"%>
				
				<span class="sms">
					<%=link_to "发送激活码","javascript:void(0)",:"data-url"=>send_sms_code_card_path,:class=>"btn",:id=>"send_sms_code"%>
					<span class="tip sms_tip"></span>
				</span>
			</div>
			<div class="field">
				<label class="field-label "><span class="required">*</span>激活码 : </label>
				<%=text_field_tag :sms_code,"",:class=>"field-input"%>
				<span class="error"><%=@card.errors.messages[:sms_code].join(",") if @card.errors.messages[:sms_code]%></span>
				<div class="green-tip">注意：验证码将会在30分钟后失效。</div>
			</div>

			<div class="field">
				<%=f.submit "确认提交",:class=>"btn submit"%>
			</div>

		<%end%>

	</div>
	<div class="tips-block">
		<p>小贴士</p>
		<ul>
			<li>
				<strong>如何激活我的VIP卡?</strong>
				<div>答：</div>
			</li>
			<li>
				<strong>怎么用VIP卡里面的余额付款?</strong>
				<div>答：</div>
			</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
	<div class="clear"></div>
	<div class="other-tip "> <span class="required">*</span> 小贴士 :  如果在激活过程中有什么疑问，请致电寻求帮助。客服电话：400-826-4568。</div>
	
</div>